Delta State Governor Dr Ifeanyi Okowa has sent seven names of Commissioner nominees to the Delta State House of Assembly for screening and confirmation as members of the State Executive Council. Delta Speaker, Sheriff Oborevwori, on Tuesday at plenary read the names following correspondence from Okowa. The governor also appointed Paul Aghalemu as Auditor General of the State. The commissioner nominees are: FidelisTilije, Mr. Lawrence Ejiofor, Barry Pere Gbe, Julius Egbedi,Mr Churchill Amagada, Mr Arthur Akpowowo and Martin Okonta. Details shortlyâ€¦